Class APIBasedInfoProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • fixed2free.integration.APIBasedInfoProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFileInfoProvider, org.rpgleparser.api.ListApiCallback

    public class APIBasedInfoProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFileInfoProvider, org.rpgleparser.api.ListApiCallback
    Uses the AS400 APIS (QUSLOBJ, QUSLRCD, QUSLFLD) to return information about a given file be it a display file, printer file, or database file
    Author:
    Eric N. Wilson
